EMULATED: Pylons is a true old school First Person Shooter where you can free roam the map to complete missions as an Anti Virus Unit operative in cyberspace.\n\nMake sure that you have a gamepad before you download! \nFor more information about gamepads see http://emulated.southpac.co/controllers/\n\nGame is set in the future when humanity exists in a cyberspace. As an operative you are assigned a mission to capture communication pylons in a city infested by Vektorbots.\n\nIncludes 6 missions with unique maps + Training mission. \n\nFeatures:\n- Story driven game\n- Advanced, futuristic shooting\n- 9 types of weapons with different characteristics\n- Elements of quest\n- Cyberpunk style graphics and environment\n- Most remote bluetooth controllers supported\n\nEMULATED: Pylons is the first of the EMULATED game series.\n\nThis game uses Southpac's VR FPS engine that minimizes the cybersicknes so you can finally walk and jump without teleporting.", "short_description": "Cyberpunk First Person Shooter. Get emulated into the system core, defeat Vektorbots and capture communication pylons. Gamepad required."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://emulated.southpac.co/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://emulated.southpac.co/terms-of-service/", "publisher_name": "Southpac Interactive", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://emulated.southpac.co/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ACTION", "SHOOTER", "PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GAMEPAD", "GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interact